{"tid":422541,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港邊度有隔音耳塞賣??","createTime":"2017-10-03T06:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T08:52:05.000Z","uid":115525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c978240a57f1872dfd7afc880f737c08b186c2fa","tid":422541,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"話說我隔離屋條死廢老撞聾又開住門睇電視<br />\n我自己閂埋門都聽到電視BGM 個D嗚嗚聲既低音聲<br />\n<br />\n我想問香港邊度有戴落舒服既 隔音耳塞賣??<br />\n隔音耳罩 由於我偏向側訓<br />\n所以戴唔到 (同埋3M個D 用得耐個罩D黑色膠就會甩)<br />\n<br />\n日本城橙色個D 戴住側訓又唔舒服 而且長條型又怕側訓會隊入耳膜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知邊度買D 靚D戴得舒服既耳塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb476ceaa623bdf3c04d8aff6eb2d11c6903a584","tid":422541,"uid":66679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e33428e75cd713fb6b7af5acd33b75273d48899","tid":422541,"uid":115525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五金鋪</blockquote><br />\n我去過兩間五金鋪 都係賣 日本城或者3M 普通橙色長條型個D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSNobYqww3t4JIHWym3DuYERp4e4aYNKFi86vfefFkFAaA7-IjT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSNobYqww3t4JIHWym3DuYERp4e4aYNKFi86vfefFkFAaA7-IjT&h=389644d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係呢D戴得唔舒服"},{"pid":"55232d0a43c36d318b851a8b5008f2b709d52145","tid":422541,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"同管理處投訴得唔得"},{"pid":"00c776baa3c2f3b9ccb5bb8a96560a1e7b180a3f","tid":422541,"uid":19910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"買個bass 番黎 不過11點前唔好聽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96eaff7a62fe8f843891f02841e403a98510a33","tid":422541,"uid":9566,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"又要隔音 又要舒服 咁你不如吉穿個耳膜啦"},{"pid":"52e19521c2f5de30df3129a737c19f5d665a7ca0","tid":422541,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:29:41.000Z","msg":"投訴佢老母咪得"},{"pid":"72d14d4ecffef9de6863a23b11ae9cc672a72517","tid":422541,"uid":115525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"投訴已經試過<br />\n一係個管理員上到黎笠水<br />\n話係善意提醒 <br />\n<br />\n一係 唔夠一陣 個廢老又開返大聲<br />\np.s. 個廢老屋企 電視向住門 所以好撚應聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報警? 又未到11點/分貝大到受理<br />\n我知有400章第5條<br />\n條例第5條賦權當局管制於日間或夜間<strong>任何時間</strong>在住用處所或公眾地方內發出的某些噪音。這類噪音源包括動物、雀鳥、樂器、揚聲器、遊戲、經營生意或業務和冷氣機等噪音。<br />\n教撚埋阿SIR做野都唔撚做  話都唔係好大聲姐  未去到&quot;噪音&quot;既標準<br />\n再話投訴埋條仆街警犬 都唔知幾時先有得早訓<br />\n所以先想買耳塞頂住先<br />\n<br />\n亦已經試過行過去直接屌柒個廢老<br />\n根本無用<br />\n廢老會聽人講野唔聞塞就唔會叫廢老啦"}]}